author: Kelsey Hendrix
title: Rookie Solveig rocks lace and leather for Flaunt Magazine - Swim Daily
text:
by Kelsey Hendrix Posted: Wed Sep. 30, 2015 Looks like Flaunt Magazine knows what's hot! Enlisting the help of SI Swimsuit rookie Solveig Mork Hansen , the once luxury fashion title turned full-fledged lifestyle publication showcases some of fall's hottest trends: lace, leather and denim.
Photo: Justin Campbell/Flaunt Magazine
Photo: Justin Campbell/Flaunt Magazine â€¢ Get wet and wild with Solveig in her 2015 SI Swimsuit outtakes!
And who better to make cooler weather appealing than our Danish beauty? Sizzling in this editorial, Solveig poses on train tracks, old rail cars and on top of vintage cars, as she channels her inner bad girl for the sultry spread.
Photo: Justin Campbell/Flaunt Magazine
Photo: Justin Campbell/Flaunt Magazine
Photo: Justin Campbell/Flaunt Magazine
Styled by Monty Jackson, Solveig makes couture looks from designers like Dior, Saint Lauren and Philipp Plein look like relatable streetwear that we can all get on board with. Cheers to our rookie for making fall (and then winter) a little less daunting!
See some of Solveig's best moments from SI Swimsuit 2015!
